{"tid":2032692,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"喺網店「香港二樓書店」買書安唔安全？？","createTime":"2020-05-24T07:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T04:45:07.000Z","uid":167619,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"13a17d5dfc7b1254f341d3b7ecbd0c156a78fbab","tid":2032692,"uid":167619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"見個網有好多書揀<br />\n但係個網站設計好似返左去20年前咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最重要係個網仲要冇加密 <br />\n要入個人資料都係冇HTTPS......<br />\n想問有冇人試過係呢個網買書？<br />\n要買D反共書又安唔安全？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacc0104fc3e583399bba4e2b676a1ad83d5e83e","tid":2032692,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:10:56.000Z","msg":"好難講，廿四小時有國安mon住個網嘅network traffic都唔出奇，你一上個網已經捕到你ip address<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c27f77d1a5f017ebac170c1d9e622a864983a8f","tid":2032692,"uid":167619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bacc0104fc3e583399bba4e2b676a1ad83d5e83e","tid":2032692,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:10:56.000Z","msg":"好難講，廿四小時有國安mon住個網嘅network traffic都唔出奇，你一上個網已經捕到你ip address<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:15:14.000Z","msg":"有用VPN<br />\n比較擔心網主會唔會篤灰<br />\n或者個網站會唔會被取締<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c62aaaa72926b89ef5b471d95b60613dfe91724","tid":2032692,"uid":167619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:30:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab16c807ad889c9f6f38c5f5e06867c6b02ba2b1","tid":2032692,"uid":259191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"上年買過, 但唔係反共書..<br />\n上門取貨, 無咩問題"},{"pid":"3f5dd650f0acad9c90af02bc4a4384cb53c1c10b","tid":2032692,"uid":167619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab16c807ad889c9f6f38c